{"tid":329910,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"諗住係Youtube 開個channel 教DSE ECON,唔知大家有無趣興睇?","createTime":"2017-07-20T17:37:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T08:18:41.000Z","uid":29740,"like":32,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b732b7fff4403450595745e00220e90717ce3f62","tid":329910,"uid":29740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T17:37:38.000Z","msg":"開錯台重開<br />\n如果大家係預我教大家咩ECON 神技,咩ECON 必殺技既話可以上一頁<br />\n無論DSE ECON又好,AL ECON 又好, CE ECON 又好.<br />\n其實考既內容都唔係太深. <br />\n所以理論上係夠時間讀識晒成個課程<br />\n唔計背野個D,其實DSE ECON 只係將一啲ECON 理倫套用返係唔同題目<br />\n如果你識晒D理論,同運用返係唔同題目到,其實最少都有5*<br />\n<br />\n大家有無咩覺得特別難既TOPICS, 如果有既話我可以先拍.<br />\n但我應該會10月頭先放第一條片,係出年DSE ECON 考試前會拍晒<br />\n<br />\n最後各位巴絲一定會問,你邊位?憑咩教ECON,一陣教錯晒點算.<br />\n所以都係利申返,本人HK ALEVEL ECON 拎A. 大學讀ECON FIRST HON. <br />\n不是係香港讀大學<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過如果大家無興趣既話都無謂嘥大家時間<br />\n唔知大家有咩興趣?"},{"pid":"62d3131c6f747e0c74ad79a92ded3efe58a6c34d","tid":329910,"uid":25496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T17:53:03.000Z","msg":"歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想自修下dse econ 係asso讀完 發現自己有啲興趣讀 想學多啲"},{"pid":"77c68a6ec314fc1db09c145e495087101b5a0a78","tid":329910,"uid":11506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T19:15:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想自修下dse econ 係asso讀完 發現自己有啲興趣讀 想學多啲</blockquote><br />\nDse econ=rubbish"},{"pid":"8c53eba23408b2d437f01d6b2b1d12495500cf7f","tid":329910,"uid":1161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T03:44:25.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"8e1bde23fb3b9663edb7dca028c6bd362fe69297","tid":329910,"uid":29740,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T09:01:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想自修下dse econ 係asso讀完 發現自己有啲興趣讀 想學多啲</blockquote><br />\nDse econ=rubbish</blockquote